======================================================================
PART 5: THE 7-21-63 PATTERN -- REPUNIT STRUCTURE
======================================================================
  7, 21, 63 = 7*1, 7*3, 7*9 = 7*3^0, 7*3^1, 7*3^2
  = 7 * {1, 3, 9} = 7 * powers of 3
  Next would be: 7 * 27 = 189 = max(H at n=7)!
  Is 189 forbidden? False
  No! 189 IS achieved (it's the maximum). The pattern breaks at 7*3^3.

  7*3^k series: 7, 21, 63, 189, 567, ...
  At n=7: 7 FORBIDDEN, 21 FORBIDDEN, 63 FORBIDDEN, 189 ACHIEVED (max)
  The forbidden pattern is 7*3^k for 0 <= k <= 2
  And 7*3^3 = 189 is the MAXIMUM value -- the pattern terminates!

  Max/Mean = 189/78.75 = 2.4000
  Min/Mean = 1/78.75 = 0.012698

